&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a role that motivates and challenges you? Are you ready for an opportunity for growth? Do you want to work on teams where people roll up their sleeves to take on tough problems together, and regularly blow the doors off our clients with their outstanding teamwork? If you answered yes to those questions, 3Cloud might just be for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At 3Cloud, we hire people who aren’t afraid to experiment or fail. We hire people who are willing to give direct and candid feedback to their managers, leaders, and team members. We hire people who jump at those opportunities because they care about our collective growth and success. We hire people who challenge and hold each other accountable for living 3Cloud’s core values because they know that it will result in amazing experiences and solutions for our clients and each other.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Manager&lt;/strong&gt; – Delivery Management&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3Cloud, A Cognizant Company, is an Azure-focused professional services firm helping clients transform their business through the power of the cloud. We specialize in Microsoft Azure to help clients accelerate innovation, operate more efficiently, and be more responsive to their customers&#39; needs. As a Microsoft partner, we specialize in Azure Migration, Application Modernization and Development, Internet of Things, AI, and DevOps achieved through Azure-Enabled Infrastructure Automation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a remote-based role in a US-based location only. &lt;strong&gt;Travel up to 20%.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Delivery Manager in Delivery Management is responsible for coordinating delivery across multiple projects or workstreams, ensuring consistency, predictability, and strong client outcomes. At this level, you operate as a delivery orchestrator — setting the cadence and standards that Lead Project Managers and their teams execute against, and stepping in directly when complex risks, dependencies, or client conversations require it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Building on the execution focus of a Lead Project Manager, the Delivery Manager broadens scope from a single engagement to multi-project / multi-workstream coordination. You mentor Lead PMs and delivery teams, drive delivery governance across engagements, contribute consultatively to client outcomes, and help shape the standards and methodologies used across the Delivery Management community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You own delivery health across multiple concurrent engagements, ensuring consistent execution, predictable reporting, and effective management of cross-team dependencies and risks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own delivery across multiple concurrent engagements or workstreams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistency in delivery execution and reporting across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage cross-team dependencies, risks, and escalations to keep delivery on track.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assess parallel or competing change initiatives that may cause change saturation, and develop strategies to minimize delivery risk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team &amp;amp; Capability Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You grow the capability of the delivery organization by mentoring Lead Project Managers and delivery teams, and by helping shape the standards that the broader Delivery Management community operates against.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor Lead Project Managers and delivery teams on delivery practices and client engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model servant leadership and provide frequent, honest feedback that helps team members grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to community leadership and the development of delivery standards across the practice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt

