nships with product, engineering, and technology leaders, and help shape&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;modernization roadmaps in the client’s best interest.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;• Provide architecture oversight so designs, interfaces, and integration points support predictable&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;delivery and stable team vel

