&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IP Development and Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Help evolve and maintain standardized models, templates, and reusable assets that improve quality and repeatability of advisory engagements.&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Integrate AI-driven insights and automation into assessment workflows where applicable.&lt;br&gt;•&amp;nbsp;Support internal initiatives to enhance delivery velocity and client experience.&lt;/p

